 7. Hu7-jin5-lang5 kap Hau7-siN hou7 Chhai5 long5 jip8
 Teng2 chiuN e5 tai7-chi3 liau2-au7 koh u7 chit8 chiah chhai5-long5 jip lang5, beh ka7 khi3 chiah8. U7 chit8-ke e5 lang5, si7 choh-sit lang5, in chit8 e5 chhin-lang5 lai5 in tau choe3 lang5-kheh, au7 lai5 beh to3-khi3, choh-sit lang5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap nng7-e5 hau7-siN chiong kiaN5 seh e5 chhia, pak8 nng7 chiah be2, chai3 i saN, si3 phou3 lou7 kau3 koaiN7 siaN5. Ti7 hia u7 thih lou7, chhin-lang5 thang tah he2-hun-chhia to3-khi3 i e5 chhu3. Seh kham3 lou7 kau7-kau7, na7 tah8 jih8 kau3 teng7-teng7, chiu7 kiaN5 seh e5 be2-chhia si7 chin7 gau5 chau2, saN ,si3 phou3 lou7 kiam2-chhai2 m7-sai2 nng7 tiam2 cheng ku2 chiu7 oe7 kau3; na7-si7 hit-tiap8 seh put-chi2 chhim, iau2-be7 jih8 teng7, be2 tioh8 ban7-ban7 kiaN5, long2 boe7 chau2, kiam2-chhai2 tioh8 si3, gou7 tiam2-cheng ku2, chiah oe7 kiaN5 saN, si3 phou3 lou7. An2-ni teng2-pou khi2-sin kiaN5, tioh8 e7-pou chiah oe7 kau3 hit e5 koaiN7 siaN5. I2-keng sang3 chhin-lang5 khi3 che7 he2-hun-chhia, kap i saN-si5, chiu7 khi3 chhe7 siaN5 lai7 chit8 ke kou2-ku7 e5 peng5-iu2 sio tham3. Peng5-iu2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chhiaN2 in theng3-hau7 chiah8 e5-hng liau2, iah8 hou7 be2 thang chiah8 koh hioh-khun3, chiah to3-khi3, kong2, ¡§Kim-mi5 geh8 kng-kng, sui-jian5 seh kham3 toe7-bin7, iau2-ku2 bo5 put-chi2 koaN5, iah8 si7 hou7 mi5-si5 koh khah kng, ¡¨chiu7 hou7 i lau5-teh. Chit-e5 peng5-iu2 gau5 tiuN tauh siat-ke3 liah8 khim5-siu3, iah8 u7 chhi7 chit8 chiah kau2, chin toa7 chiah, koh koai-koai, piau2 i e5 mia5 kio3 choe3 But-lo3. 
 Chiah8 e5-hng liau2, choh-sit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap nng7-e5 hau7-siN khi2-sin to3-khi3, tioh8 oaN3-oaN3 poaN3-mi5 au7 chiah oe7 kau3. In-ui7 si7 sin khui e5 sou2-chai7, li7 siaN5 bo5 joa7-hng7, long2 si7 kau-ia2, bo5 jin5-ke. Toa7 hau7-siN chap8-lak8 he3, che7 thau5-cheng5 koan2-be2, khan be2-lek8-soh; lau7-bu2 kap soe3-han3 hau7-siN che7 au7-bin7. U7 geh8 koh u7 seh, sou2-i2 mi5 kng-kng, oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 hng7-hng7. Lau7-bu2 ai3 hou7 gin2-na2 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 kong2-oe7 liam7-koa gim5-si. KiaN5 kui2 li2 lou7 lau7-bu2 oat8-thau5 khoaN3 au7-bin7, chiu7 kong2, ¡§Gin2-na2 ah, lin2 khoaN3, But-lo3 teh te3 lan2, taN beh chaiN2-iuN7 hou7 i to3 khi3 ?¡¨ Nng7 e5 gin2-na2 oat8-thau5 khoaN3, toa7-han3 khoaN3 khah ku2, chiu7 bin7 piN3 toa7 kiaN, kong2, ¡§An2-ne, hit chiah m7-si7 kau2 si7 toa7 chhai5-long5; ti7 lan2 tu2-a2 keng-ke3 e5 chhiu7-na5, u7 thiaN-kiN3 lan2 e5 siaN, lai5 jip lan2. TaN kiaN-liau2 lan2 bo5 thang ng3-bang7; chit ho7 lou7, be2 long2 boe7 chau2, iah8 hit chiah chhai5-long5, teh jip lan2, li2 khoaN3, bo5 joa7-ku2 oe7 tioh8.¡¨ 
 Tai7-ke put-chi2 kiaN, khoaN3 chhia-lai7 bo5 sim2-mih8 ke-si thang koaN2 chhai5-long5 po2-hou7 ka-ki7. Chhai5-long5 khah kun7 teh hau2, be2 thiaN-kiN3 hit-e5 siaN chin7 kiaN,toa7 hau7-siN tioh8 chin7 ka-ki7 e5 khui3-lat8, chiang2-koan2 iok-sok chiah-e5 be2, long2 boe7 kou3-tit pat8-mih8 e5 tai7-chi3. Soe3-han3 khioh seh, chhut-lat8 nih choe3 chioh8-thau5, choe7-choe7 liap8 lok chhia-lai7. U7 chit8-ki thih-ki hou7 chhia be2-bin7 e5 than2-hoaiN5 pang oe7 tiau5, toa7 hau7-siN ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 pak khi2-lai5. Chhai5-long5 jip oa2, lau7-bu2 kap soe3-han3 gin2-na2 chiong chit te3 pang kap hit ki thih-ki, kiah8 beh phah, gin2-na2 u7 si5 iah8 eng7 seh lai5 tim3--i. 
 Chhai5-long5 u7 si5 oa2 chhia au7, u7 si5 toa7-peng5, u7 si5 sio2-peng5, lau7-bu2 kap soe3-han3 gin2-na2 tak8-pai2 koaN2 i li7. U7 si5 chhai5-long5 oe7 khu5-teh toa7-siaN hau2, chhin-chhiuN7 beh kio3 pat8 chiah lai5 tau3 pang-chan7; chiu7 koh-chai3 jip, lai5 oa2 chhia; in koh koaN2 i li7. 
 Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni kiaN5 chha-put-to saN phou3 lou7, chiu7 kau3 lang5 khia7-ke e5 sou2-chai7, chhai5-long5 m7-kaN2 koh te3, khoan2-sit si7 chhin-chhiuN7 toa7 sit bang7, chiu7 chhut chit8 e7 e5 kek8 toa7-siaN, chiah li7-khui to3-tng2 khi3. Hu7-jin5-lang5 nng7-e5 gin2-na2 kau3 chhu3, kaN2 u7 toa7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, hou7 in keng-ke3 chit ho7 gui5-hiam2, iah8 po2-choan5 siN3-mia7. 
 Bin5-a2-cha2-khi2 siaN5 lai7 hit e5 peng5-iu2 chhut-khi3 chhiu7-na5 kau-ia2 beh khi3 khoaN3 i e5 tauh-a2 ke3-a2 u7 tng-tioh8 sim2-mih8 mih8, chiu7 ti7 lou7 nih8 khoaN3-kiN3 chhai5-long5 e5 kha-jiah, u7-si5 lou7 e5 chiaN3-chhiu2 peng5, u7-si5 to3-chhiu2-peng5, ka-ki7 phah-sng3 u7 kui2-na7 chiah-e5 chhai5-long5, cha7-mi5 khi3 ka7 hit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap nng7 e5 gin2-na2, na7 u7 an2-ni tek-khak saN lang5 long2 u7 ka7-si2. I chiu7 kin2-kin2 to3-khi3 siaN5 lai7, kio3 kui2-na7 e5 chhu3-piN, giah8 chheng3 khia5 be2, kin2-kin2 khi3 chha5 hit tiau5-lou7, siong5-siong5 phah-sng3 oe7 liam5-piN tu2-tioh8 huih, a2-si7 bah, a2-si7 kut-thau5, a2-si7 saN-a2-khou3 ti7 lou7-piN, choe3 pin5-ku3 lang5 hou7 chhai5-long5 ka7 khi3 chiah8. Chhe7 long2 bo5 chit ho7 e5 tai7-chi3; kiaN5 hng7-hng7, chiu7 khoaN3-kiN3 chhai5-long5 e5 kha-jiah soah, toa7 ki5-koai3 kin2-kin2 khi3 peng5-iu2 e5 chhu3 khoaN3 tai7-chi3 chaiN2-iuN7, khoaN3-kiN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap nng7 e5 gin2-na2, seng-khu bo5 siaN2-su7, na7-si7 sim-koaN iau2-ku2 teh-chhoah e5 khoan2-sit. Tai7-ke thiaN hu7-jin5-lang5 kap gin2-na2 siong5-se3 kong2-khi2 cha7-mi5 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7 koh kiah8 chheng3 khia5-be2 kin2-kin2 chhe7 hit-chiah chhai5-long5, chhe7-tioh8, phah si2, pak phe5 sang3 hou7 hit nng7 e5 gin2-na2, hou7 in thang khi3 ge5-mng5, tho2 thai5 chhai5-long5 e5 siuN2, chiau3 hit sou2-chai7 e5 hoat-tou7, chiu7-si7 chap8-khou. 
 Seng3-chheh choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 kong2-khi2 chhai5-long5 e5 tai7-chi3. Lang5 choe3 kau3-hoe7 e5 tui3-tek8 lai5 khun2-tiok8 Siong7-te3 e5 peh-siN3, a2-si7 choe3 koaN oan-ong2 lek8-sek lang5, a2-si7 choe3 ke2 e5 sian-siN thoan5 iN7-toan e5 ka3-si7 in2-iu2 lang5 li7-khui chin-li2, chit-ho7 lang5 Seng3-chheh kio3 choe3 chhai5-long5. (KhoaN3 se. 22 :27; Hoan. 3 : 3; Ma2. 7:15; 10: 16; Lou7. 10: 3; Su3. 20: 29 ) Seng3-chheh kong2 au7-lai5 hok-im e5 to7-li2 liu5-thong, ban7-kok e5 lang5 hang5-hok8 Ia5-sou, saN-thai5 e5 tai7-chi3 soah, thiN e7 tak8 sou2-chai7 peng5-tiaN7, chiu7 eng7 phi3-ju7, kong2 chhai5-long5 iuN5-ko oe7 saN kap toa3 saN kap chiah8. long2 bo5 siong-hai7 (KhoaN3 Sai3 11:6; 65:25.) Goan7 Siong7-te3 hou7 hit ho7 e5 si5-chun7 kin2-kin2 kau3. Sim sou2 goan7. 
 8. Lou5-pok8 hou7 Chhai5-long5 ka7 Si2, lai5 kiu3 Chu2-lang5
 U7 thiaN-kiN3 kou2-cha2 e5 si5, ti7 Go5-lo5-su kok, u7 chit8 e5 toa7-lo2, in-ui7 iau3-kin2 e5 tai7-chi3, beh khi3 hng7-hng7 e5 sou2-chai7. Hit-tiap8 si7 jit8-am3 e5 si5, chiu7 kio3 i e5 lou5-pok8, mia5 kio3 I2-lip8, ka7 i kong2, ¡§I2-lip8 ah, lan2 chit-tiap8 koaN2-kin2 beh chhut-lou7 khi3 , li2 tioh8 pi7-pan7 be2-chhia m7-thang ian5-chhian5.¡¨ Bo5 chit8-tiap8-a2 ku2 I2-lip8 chiu7 kong2 pi7-pan7 ho2-se3. Toa7-lo2 kap i e5 bou2 kiaN2 sui5-si5 chiu7 che7 chhia; I2-lip8 ia7 che7 ti7 chhia cheng5, khan be2-soh, chek-si5 khi2-sin. 
 Hit-tiap8 si7 tang-thiN e5 si5, moa2 thiN u7 chhiN put-chi2 kng. In kiaN5 kau3 lou7-cham7, chiu7 hioh-khun3, ai3 beh oaN7 be2; in-ui7 ti7 lou7 nih8 seh chin kau7, be2 kiaN5 kek8 sian7, kau3 beh poah8-to2; ia7 si7 in-ui7 kiaN5 kau3 poaN3-mi5-lah. Hit e5 lou7-cham7 e5 tiam3 chu2 chiu7 khng3 toa7-lo2 theng3-hau7 kau3 thiN phu2 kng chiah kiaN5, kong2, ¡§M7-tan7-na7 seh kau7, thiN-khi3 chin koaN5, ia7 u7 chhai5-long5 kui-kun5 pian3 si3-koe3 kiaN5. Kui2-na7 le2-pai3 ku2 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 bo5 sim2-mih8 thang chiah8. E5-hng beh am3 e5 si5, goan2 u7 thiaN-kiN3 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5, ti7 hng7-hng7 e5 chhiu7-na5 teh hau2. Kui2-na7 mi5 cheng5 u7 chhai5-long5 lai5 ti7 chia si2-koe3 seh8 toa7 siaN hau2, ai3 beh chhe7 chiah8 e5 mih8. Goa2 m7-kaN2 khui mng5, na7 chhut khi3 tek-khak peh8-peh8 sang3 goa2 e5 siN3-mia7; goa2 u7 khui thang-a2 khoaN3 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 bak8-chiu kim-kim siong3 hou7 goa2 kiaN kau3 ngauh8-ngauh8-chhoah, goa2 kau3 chit8-si3-lang5 to oe7 ki3-tit. Kau3 thiN phu2 kng chhai5-long5 chiah soaN3 khi3. 
 Toa7-lo2 thiaN-kiN3 i sou2 kong2, sim7-sim7 chit8-tiap8-a2 ku2; che m7-si7 i ka-ki7 u7 kiaN, si7 in-ui7 u7 bou2, kiaN2 ti7-teh, sou2-i2 kiaN-hiaN5, u7 chin3-the3 liong2-lan5 e5 i3-su3, chiu7 in3 tiam3 chu2 kong2, ¡§Goa2 phah-sng3 thang koh ke kiaN5 chit8 lou7-cham7, in-ui7 goa2 e5 lou5-pok8 put-chi2 iong2-beng2, ia7 u7 toa7 kek8 ho2 e5 chheng3, li2 tioh8 pi7-pan7 kek8 iong2 kek8 gau5-chau2 e5 be2 lai5 hou7 goa2 oaN7 chiu7 ho2.¡¨ Tiam3 chu2 chek-si5 chiong iong2 e5 be2 lai5 pak8 ti7 chhia nih8. I2-lip8 ia7 sui5-si5 chiuN7 chhia ho2-taN2 khan be2-soh iat be2 piN liam5-piN khi2-sin khi3. Chit8 li2 kiaN5 ke3 chit8 li2, long2 bo5 tong7-cheng7, tok8-tok8 thiaN-kiN3 be2 long e5 siaN na7-tiaN7. 
 Au7-lai5 kiaN5 kau3 chit8 e5 toa7 chhiu7-na5, hit sou2-chai7 chhiN-chhiN chhin3-chhin3, chhiu7 chin koaiN5 kau3 tu2-thiN jia-tioh8 chhiN-sin5, sou2-i2 chit sou2-chai7 chin-am3. In beh ke3 chit e5 chhiu7-na5 e5 lou7 na2 kiaN5 na2 am3. Kau3 chia chu2, pok8 long2 m7-kaN2 choe3 siaN, in-ui7 u7 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 keng-ke3 chit tiau5 lou7, choe7-choe7 tu2-tioh8 chhai5-long5, sit-liau2 siN3-mia7. 
 KiaN5 bo5 kui2-pou7 hut-jian5 thiaN-kiN3 chin hiong-beng2 e5 siaN, I2-lip8 chai chit e5 siaN m7-si7 chhiu7-na5 e5 hong, ia7 m7-si7 hong tui3 soaN-teng2 lai5, tek-khak si7 iau-go7 hiong5-ok e5 chhai5-long5 si3-koe3 kiaN5 teh hau2. I2-lip8 chai taN tu2-tioh8 ti7 chia siN3-mia7 tek-khak lan5 po2, chiu7 oat8-thau5 lai5 phah-chhia nih8 e5 thang-a2-mng5, beh thong-ti i e5 chu2-lang5 chai chit e5 tai7-chi3. Toa7-lo2 chiu7 an-ui3 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, ¡§M7-sai2 kiaN, tioh8 oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3.¡¨ Hu7-jin5-lang5 thiaN in tiong7-hu e5 oe7, chiu7 pho7 i e5 kiaN2, the ti7 chhia-lai7, seng5-sim ki5-to2 choan5-leng5 e5 Siong7-te3 chiau3-kou3 i e5 tiong7-hu kap kiaN2 chit8 ke peng5-an. I2-lip8 chiu7 chhut-lat8 phah be2 koaN2 chin3-cheng5 chau2 khi3. Chai chit e5 tai7-chi3 put-chi2 gui5-hiam2, chhai5-long5 tek-khak oe7 tui-jip lai5; taN beh chau2, a2-si7 beh kap chhai5-long5 tui3-tek8, a2-si7 tioh8 si2, siuN7 boe7 hiau2-tit. Chhai5-long5 e5 siaN na2 thiaN na2 kun7, lian5 kha-pou7 ia7 thiaN-kiN3, i2-keng kau3 ti7 chhia-au7. 
 Au7-lai5 chhai5-long5 tui kau3 kun7-oa2, khoaN3-kiN3 chhia nih8 e5 teng kng-kng, chiu7 theng5-kha, m7-kaN2 koh tui lai5. Tiap8-a2-ku2 chhai5-long5 koh-chai3 ho2-taN2 si3-ui5 pau chit tiuN chhia. Chhia nih8 e5 teng chio3 tioh8 chhai5-long5, khoaN3-kiN3 kui-kun5, seng-khu kek8 san2, bak8-chiu kim-kim, chhui3 khui-khui, chih8 thou3 tng5-tng5, noa7 it-tit8 lau5 chhut-lai5. Toa7-lo2 chiu7 kong2, ¡§I2-lip8 ah, lan2 tioh8 pang3 chheng3. Li2 tioh8 siong3 cheng-cheng, chheng3 chiah thang khui-khi3. ¡¨ Hut-jian5 hit chiah choe3 thau5 e5 chhai5-long5 hou7 chheng3 phah si2, to2 ti7 seh nih8 moa2 sin si7 huih. Ki5-u5 e5 chhai5-long5 thiaN-kiN3 chheng3 e5 siaN, koh khoaN3-kiN3 thau5-chiah si2-teh, u7 chin toa7 kiaN si3-koe3 to5-chau2 jip8 ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7, boe7 kou3-tit thang chiah8 hit chiah si2 e5 chhai5-long5. 
 Bo5 chit8-khek ku2 chhai5-long5 koh chu7-chip8 kui-kun5 ui5-lai5, pi2 cheng5 khah hiong5-ok. In-ui7 chiah-e5 chhai5-long5 chin iau sou2-i2 m7-kam pang3-sak chit tiuN be2-chhia; toa7-siaN chhoan2-khui3 siuN7 beh lai5 ka7 chiah8. I2-lip8 chiu7 koh phah si2 chit8 chiah; hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 theng5 kha teh-hau2, bo5 sim2-mih8 kiaN-hiaN5, ia7 bo5 chau2 khi3. Koh pek-kun7 oa2-lai5, chhui3-khi2 giang3-giang3, toa7-siaN teh hau2. I2-lip8 khoaN3-kiN3 m7-si7 se3 bin7, chiu7 siuN7 taN beh chaiN2-iuN7 ? In-ui7 tioh8 koh kiaN5 chin hng7 chiah oe7 kau3 lou7-cham7. Hit-tiap8 ti7 chhia-nih8 u7 chit8 ki chha5, chiu7 eng7 soh lai5 pak8, hiat ti7 chhia-au7 hou7 chhia teh thoa, hou7 hit ki chha5 tin2-tang7 pong7-pong7 hau2, beh koaN2-soaN3 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5. Na7-si7 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 long2 chai si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 mih8, iu5-goan5 m7 kiaN bo5 beh si3-soaN3 khi3, pi2 cheng5 koh khah beng2. 
 Kau3 chit-tiap8 hit tiuN chhia e5 lang5 siN3-mia7 i2-keng bo5 ng3-bang7. I2-lip8 chiu7 ka7 i e5 lou7-pok8 phoaN7 kong2, ¡§Thau5 chiah be2 tioh8 thau2, kin2-kin2 thau2. ¡¨Sui5-si5 chiong thau5 chiah-e5 be2 thau2-khui; hit chiah be2 u7 chin kiaN, chhoan3 tui7 lou7-piN chau2-khi3. Chhai5-long5 kui-kun5 tui3 hit chiah be2 chiu7 jip khi3, saN-kap ka7 hit chiah be2 tau3 chhiuN2 khi3 chiah8. Siong7-chhiaN2 bo5 kau3-giah8, u7 chiah8 tam7-poh8 huih, pak-tou2 iau2-ku2 si7 iau, kui-kun5 koh te3 be2-chhia lai5, Chong2-si7 be2-chhia i2-keng u7 chin3-cheng5 kiaN5 kui2-na7 li2 lou7 ke3--khi3. 
 Toa7-lo2 chiu7 kong2, ¡§I2-lip8 ah, lan2 chit-tiap8 sou2 thiaN-kiN3 si7 chhiu7-nih8 e5 hong mah ? A2-si7 hiah-e5 beng2 e5 chhai5-long5 koh te3-lai5 mah ?¡¨ I2-lip8 tai7-seng ia7 u7 thiaN-kiN3, i chai si7 chhai5-long5 e5 siaN, Chong2-si7 i put-chi2 thiaN3 chu2-lang5, m7 kam hou7 in tai7-ke kiaN-hiaN5, sou2-i2 long2 bo5 kong2-chhut. In-ui7 i e5 chu2-lang5 mng7-khi2, I2-lip8 in3 i, kong2, ¡§Chiu7-si7 hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 koh tui lai5. ¡¨Oe7 tu2 kong2-liau2, hiah-e5 chhai5-long5 koh si3 ui5 lai5 pau chit tiuN chhia. Chhai5-long5 e5 heng5-chong7 pi2 tai7-seng teng5-pe7 phaiN2 khoaN3, in-ui7 tak8 chiah seng-khu long2 u7 bak-huih. 
 I2-lip8 chiu7 kong2, ¡§Koh thau2 thau5 chiah-e5 be2.¡¨ Soh tu2 thau2-khui, be2 chiu7 chau2; chi2 u7 thiaN-kiN3 be2 hau2 chit8 siaN, i2-keng khoaN3-bo5, hit chiah be2 chiu7-si7 hou7 chhai5-long5 sui5-si5 chiah8-liau2 khi3. Chhai5-long5 iau2-ku2 si7 iau, tek-khak ai3 beh koh chiah8 lang5 e5 huih. 
